02:38.658 --> 02:39.534
The carriage house.

02:39.617 --> 02:42.328
So, the carriage house
is 2,400 square feet,

02:42.412 --> 02:44.789
and it has two possible rental units.

02:44.873 --> 02:46.958
The first floor, I think,
could be one unit.

02:47.041 --> 02:49.586
