03:49.062 --> 03:51.606
the two big carriage doors.

03:52.774 --> 03:54.317
-Hey!
-Hi!

03:54.400 --> 03:56.527
-Hi, nice to meet you--
-Alex, nice to meet you.

03:56.611 --> 03:58.529
-Pleasure.
-How you doing?

03:58.613 --> 04:01.032
Look at your lady.
