11:21.722 --> 11:23.391
Let's talk about what's going where,

11:23.474 --> 11:25.976
'cause we need to start construction
on everything.

11:27.853 --> 11:31.565
To convert this into
a short-term, we've got to make this feel

11:31.649 --> 11:33.693
