13:01.113 --> 13:02.323
Okay...

13:02.406 --> 13:06.702
We don't have that kind of money to spend
but I think I've got an idea.

13:06.786 --> 13:12.541
You happen to be located in the king town
of antiques and furniture and art.

13:12.625 --> 13:15.377
If you think of your B&amp;B

13:15.461 --> 13:19.715
much like an antique store
or on-consignment store,

13:19.799 --> 13:25.846
