13:42.196 --> 13:45.032
It's kind of a boutique experience
and it's free for you,

13:45.115 --> 13:46.450
and we don't have a lot
of choice.

13:46.534 --> 13:50.496
Because Hudson is Hudson,
people come here to go antiquing,

13:50.579 --> 13:53.999
so that they can sleep in a place
that's full of antiques,

13:54.083 --> 13:56.794
so sleeping and antiquing
at the same time.

13:56.877 --> 13:58.754
I see a marketing ploy.

13:58.838 --> 14:02.842
